      "code": null,
      "value": null,
      "unit": null,
      "effective": null,
      "source_ref": "note:row465683#s2",
      "text": "She was DC d home and    then had reoccurrence of chest pain 2 days later, ruled in at [**Hospital1 4328**] for STEMI ( Inferior MI)."
